{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"It feels like we're all suffering"},{"time":2000,"text":"from information overload or data glut."},{"time":5000,"text":"And the good news is there might be an easy solution to that,"},{"time":7000,"text":"and that's using our eyes more."},{"time":9000,"text":"So, visualizing information, so that we can see"},{"time":11000,"text":"the patterns and connections that matter"},{"time":14000,"text":"and then designing that information so it makes more sense,"},{"time":17000,"text":"or it tells a story,"},{"time":19000,"text":"or allows us to focus only on the information that's important."},{"time":23000,"text":"Failing that, visualized information can just look really cool."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26000,"text":"So, let's see."},{"time":30000,"text":"This is the $Billion Dollar o-Gram,"},{"time":32000,"text":"and this image arose"},{"time":34000,"text":"out of frustration I had"},{"time":36000,"text":"with the reporting of billion-dollar amounts in the press."},{"time":38000,"text":"That is, they're meaningless without context:"},{"time":41000,"text":"500 billion for this pipeline,"},{"time":43000,"text":"20 billion for this war."},{"time":45000,"text":"It doesn't make any sense, so the only way to understand it"},{"time":47000,"text":"is visually and relatively."},{"time":49000,"text":"So I scraped a load of reported figures"},{"time":51000,"text":"from various news outlets"},{"time":53000,"text":"and then scaled the boxes according to those amounts."},{"time":56000,"text":"And the colors here represent the motivation behind the money."},{"time":59000,"text":"So purple is \"fighting,\""},{"time":62000,"text":"and red is \"giving money away,\" and green is \"profiteering.\""},{"time":65000,"text":"And what you can see straight away"},{"time":67000,"text":"is you start to have a different relationship to the numbers."},{"time":69000,"text":"You can literally see them."},{"time":71000,"text":"But more importantly, you start to see"},{"time":73000,"text":"patterns and connections between numbers"},{"time":75000,"text":"that would otherwise be scattered across multiple news reports."}]},{"cues":[{"time":78000,"text":"Let me point out some that I really like."},{"time":81000,"text":"This is OPEC's revenue, this green box here --"},{"time":83000,"text":"780 billion a year."},{"time":85000,"text":"And this little pixel in the corner -- three billion --"},{"time":88000,"text":"that's their climate change fund."},{"time":91000,"text":"Americans, incredibly generous people --"},{"time":93000,"text":"over 300 billion a year, donated to charity every year,"},{"time":96000,"text":"compared with the amount of foreign aid"},{"time":98000,"text":"given by the top 17 industrialized nations"},{"time":100000,"text":"at 120 billion."},{"time":102000,"text":"Then of course,"},{"time":104000,"text":"the Iraq War, predicted to cost just 60 billion"},{"time":106000,"text":"back in 2003."},{"time":109000,"text":"And it mushroomed slightly. Afghanistan and Iraq mushroomed now"},{"time":112000,"text":"to 3,000 billion."},{"time":115000,"text":"So now it's great"},{"time":117000,"text":"because now we have this texture, and we can add numbers to it as well."},{"time":119000,"text":"So we could say, well, a new figure comes out ... let's see African debt."},{"time":122000,"text":"How much of this diagram do you think might be taken up"},{"time":124000,"text":"by the debt that Africa owes to the West?"},{"time":126000,"text":"Let's take a look."},{"time":128000,"text":"So there it is:"},{"time":130000,"text":"227 billion is what Africa owes."},{"time":132000,"text":"And the recent financial crisis,"},{"time":134000,"text":"how much of this diagram might that figure take up?"},{"time":136000,"text":"What has that cost the world? Let's take a look at that."},{"time":139000,"text":"Dooosh -- Which I think is the appropriate sound effect"},{"time":142000,"text":"for that much money:"},{"time":144000,"text":"11,900 billion."},{"time":150000,"text":"So, by visualizing this information,"},{"time":152000,"text":"we turned it into a landscape"},{"time":154000,"text":"that you can explore with your eyes,"},{"time":156000,"text":"a kind of map really, a sort of information map."},{"time":158000,"text":"And when you're lost in information,"},{"time":160000,"text":"an information map is kind of useful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163000,"text":"So I want to show you another landscape now."},{"time":165000,"text":"We need to imagine what a landscape"},{"time":167000,"text":"of the world's fears might look like."},{"time":170000,"text":"Let's take a look."},{"time":172000,"text":"This is Mountains Out of Molehills,"},{"time":174000,"text":"a timeline of global media panic."},{"time":176000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":178000,"text":"So, I'll label this for you in a second."},{"time":180000,"text":"But the height here, I want to point out,"},{"time":182000,"text":"is the intensity of certain fears"},{"time":184000,"text":"as reported in the media."},{"time":186000,"text":"Let me point them out."},{"time":188000,"text":"So this, swine flu -- pink."},{"time":192000,"text":"Bird flu."},{"time":194000,"text":"SARS -- brownish here. Remember that one?"},{"time":197000,"text":"The millennium bug,"},{"time":200000,"text":"terrible disaster."},{"time":202000,"text":"These little green peaks"},{"time":204000,"text":"are asteroid collisions."},{"time":206000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":208000,"text":"And in summer, here, killer wasps."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":218000,"text":"So these are what our fears look like"},{"time":220000,"text":"over time in our media."},{"time":222000,"text":"But what I love -- and I'm a journalist --"},{"time":224000,"text":"and what I love is finding hidden patterns; I love being a data detective."},{"time":227000,"text":"And there's a very interesting and odd pattern hidden in this data"},{"time":230000,"text":"that you can only see when you visualize it."},{"time":232000,"text":"Let me highlight it for you."},{"time":234000,"text":"See this line, this is a landscape for violent video games."},{"time":237000,"text":"As you can see, there's a kind of odd, regular pattern in the data,"},{"time":240000,"text":"twin peaks every year."},{"time":242000,"text":"If we look closer, we see those peaks occur"},{"time":244000,"text":"at the same month every year."},{"time":247000,"text":"Why?"},{"time":249000,"text":"Well, November, Christmas video games come out,"},{"time":251000,"text":"and there may well be an upsurge in the concern about their content."},{"time":254000,"text":"But April isn't a particularly massive month"},{"time":257000,"text":"for video games."},{"time":259000,"text":"Why April?"},{"time":261000,"text":"Well, in April 1999 was the Columbine shooting,"},{"time":264000,"text":"and since then, that fear"},{"time":266000,"text":"has been remembered by the media"},{"time":268000,"text":"and echoes through the group mind gradually through the year."},{"time":270000,"text":"You have retrospectives, anniversaries,"},{"time":273000,"text":"court cases, even copy-cat shootings,"},{"time":276000,"text":"all pushing that fear into the agenda."},{"time":279000,"text":"And there's another pattern here as well. Can you spot it?"},{"time":281000,"text":"See that gap there? There's a gap,"},{"time":283000,"text":"and it affects all the other stories."},{"time":285000,"text":"Why is there a gap there?"},{"time":287000,"text":"You see where it starts? September 2001,"},{"time":290000,"text":"when we had something very real"},{"time":292000,"text":"to be scared about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":294000,"text":"So, I've been working as a data journalist for about a year,"},{"time":297000,"text":"and I keep hearing a phrase"},{"time":299000,"text":"all the time, which is this:"},{"time":302000,"text":"\"Data is the new oil.\""},{"time":304000,"text":"Data is the kind of ubiquitous resource"},{"time":307000,"text":"that we can shape to provide new innovations and new insights,"},{"time":310000,"text":"and it's all around us, and it can be mined very easily."},{"time":313000,"text":"It's not a particularly great metaphor in these times,"},{"time":316000,"text":"especially if you live around the Gulf of Mexico,"},{"time":319000,"text":"but I would, perhaps, adapt this metaphor slightly,"},{"time":321000,"text":"and I would say that data is the new soil."},{"time":325000,"text":"Because for me, it feels like a fertile, creative medium."},{"time":328000,"text":"Over the years, online,"},{"time":330000,"text":"we've laid down"},{"time":333000,"text":"a huge amount of information and data,"},{"time":335000,"text":"and we irrigate it with networks and connectivity,"},{"time":337000,"text":"and it's been worked and tilled by unpaid workers and governments."},{"time":340000,"text":"And, all right, I'm kind of milking the metaphor a little bit."},{"time":343000,"text":"But it's a really fertile medium,"},{"time":346000,"text":"and it feels like visualizations, infographics, data visualizations,"},{"time":349000,"text":"they feel like flowers blooming from this medium."},{"time":352000,"text":"But if you look at it directly,"},{"time":354000,"text":"it's just a lot of numbers and disconnected facts."},{"time":356000,"text":"But if you start working with it and playing with it in a certain way,"},{"time":359000,"text":"interesting things can appear and different patterns can be revealed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":362000,"text":"Let me show you this."},{"time":364000,"text":"Can you guess what this data set is?"},{"time":367000,"text":"What rises twice a year,"},{"time":369000,"text":"once in Easter"},{"time":371000,"text":"and then two weeks before Christmas,"},{"time":373000,"text":"has a mini peak every Monday,"},{"time":375000,"text":"and then flattens out over the summer?"},{"time":377000,"text":"I'll take answers."},{"time":379000,"text":"(Audience: Chocolate.) David McCandless: Chocolate."},{"time":381000,"text":"You might want to get some chocolate in."},{"time":384000,"text":"Any other guesses?"},{"time":386000,"text":"(Audience: Shopping.) DM: Shopping."},{"time":388000,"text":"Yeah, retail therapy might help."},{"time":391000,"text":"(Audience: Sick leave.)"},{"time":393000,"text":"DM: Sick leave. Yeah, you'll definitely want to take some time off."},{"time":395000,"text":"Shall we see?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":398000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":406000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":409000,"text":"So, the information guru Lee Byron and myself,"},{"time":412000,"text":"we scraped 10,000 status Facebook updates"},{"time":415000,"text":"for the phrase \"break-up\" and \"broken-up\""},{"time":417000,"text":"and this is the pattern we found --"},{"time":419000,"text":"people clearing out for Spring Break,"},{"time":421000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":426000,"text":"coming out of very bad weekends on a Monday,"},{"time":428000,"text":"being single over the summer,"},{"time":431000,"text":"and then the lowest day of the year, of course: Christmas Day."},{"time":434000,"text":"Who would do that?"},{"time":437000,"text":"So there's a titanic amount of data out there now,"},{"time":439000,"text":"unprecedented."},{"time":442000,"text":"But if you ask the right kind of question,"},{"time":444000,"text":"or you work it in the right kind of way,"},{"time":446000,"text":"interesting things can emerge."}]},{"cues":[{"time":449000,"text":"So information is beautiful. Data is beautiful."},{"time":452000,"text":"I wonder if I could make my life beautiful."},{"time":455000,"text":"And here's my visual C.V."},{"time":457000,"text":"I'm not quite sure I've succeeded."},{"time":459000,"text":"Pretty blocky, the colors aren't that great."},{"time":461000,"text":"But I wanted to convey something to you."},{"time":464000,"text":"I started as a programmer,"},{"time":466000,"text":"and then I worked as a writer for many years, about 20 years,"},{"time":468000,"text":"in print, online and then in advertising,"},{"time":470000,"text":"and only recently have I started designing."},{"time":473000,"text":"And I've never been to design school."},{"time":475000,"text":"I've never studied art or anything."},{"time":478000,"text":"I just kind of learned through doing."},{"time":480000,"text":"And when I started designing,"},{"time":482000,"text":"I discovered an odd thing about myself."},{"time":484000,"text":"I already knew how to design,"},{"time":486000,"text":"but it wasn't like I was amazingly brilliant at it,"},{"time":489000,"text":"but more like I was sensitive"},{"time":491000,"text":"to the ideas of grids and space"},{"time":493000,"text":"and alignment and typography."},{"time":495000,"text":"It's almost like being exposed"},{"time":497000,"text":"to all this media over the years"},{"time":499000,"text":"had instilled a kind of dormant design literacy in me."},{"time":502000,"text":"And I don't feel like I'm unique."}]},{"cues":[{"time":504000,"text":"I feel that everyday, all of us now"},{"time":506000,"text":"are being blasted by information design."},{"time":509000,"text":"It's being poured into our eyes through the Web,"},{"time":511000,"text":"and we're all visualizers now;"},{"time":513000,"text":"we're all demanding a visual aspect"},{"time":515000,"text":"to our information."},{"time":518000,"text":"There's something almost quite magical about visual information."},{"time":521000,"text":"It's effortless, it literally pours in."},{"time":524000,"text":"And if you're navigating a dense information jungle,"},{"time":527000,"text":"coming across a beautiful graphic"},{"time":529000,"text":"or a lovely data visualization,"},{"time":531000,"text":"it's a relief, it's like coming across a clearing in the jungle."},{"time":534000,"text":"I was curious about this, so it led me"},{"time":536000,"text":"to the work of a Danish physicist"},{"time":538000,"text":"called Tor Norretranders,"},{"time":540000,"text":"and he converted the bandwidth of the senses into computer terms."}]},{"cues":[{"time":544000,"text":"So here we go. This is your senses,"},{"time":546000,"text":"pouring into your senses every second."},{"time":548000,"text":"Your sense of sight is the fastest."},{"time":551000,"text":"It has the same bandwidth as a computer network."},{"time":554000,"text":"Then you have touch, which is about the speed of a USB key."},{"time":557000,"text":"And then you have hearing and smell,"},{"time":559000,"text":"which has the throughput of a hard disk."},{"time":561000,"text":"And then you have poor old taste,"},{"time":563000,"text":"which is like barely the throughput of a pocket calculator."},{"time":566000,"text":"And that little square in the corner, a naught .7 percent,"},{"time":569000,"text":"that's the amount we're actually aware of."},{"time":572000,"text":"So a lot of your vision --"},{"time":574000,"text":"the bulk of it is visual, and it's pouring in."},{"time":576000,"text":"It's unconscious."},{"time":578000,"text":"The eye is exquisitely sensitive"},{"time":581000,"text":"to patterns in variations in color, shape and pattern."},{"time":584000,"text":"It loves them, and it calls them beautiful."},{"time":586000,"text":"It's the language of the eye."},{"time":588000,"text":"If you combine the language of the eye with the language of the mind,"},{"time":590000,"text":"which is about words and numbers and concepts,"},{"time":593000,"text":"you start speaking two languages simultaneously,"},{"time":596000,"text":"each enhancing the other."},{"time":599000,"text":"So, you have the eye, and then you drop in the concepts."},{"time":602000,"text":"And that whole thing -- it's two languages"},{"time":604000,"text":"both working at the same time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":606000,"text":"So we can use this new kind of language, if you like,"},{"time":608000,"text":"to alter our perspective or change our views."},{"time":611000,"text":"Let me ask you a simple question"},{"time":613000,"text":"with a really simple answer:"},{"time":615000,"text":"Who has the biggest military budget?"},{"time":617000,"text":"It's got to be America, right?"},{"time":619000,"text":"Massive. 609 billion in 2008 --"},{"time":621000,"text":"607, rather."},{"time":623000,"text":"So massive, in fact, that it can contain"},{"time":625000,"text":"all the other military budgets in the world inside itself."},{"time":628000,"text":"Gobble, gobble, gobble, gobble, gobble."},{"time":630000,"text":"Now, you can see Africa's total debt there"},{"time":632000,"text":"and the U.K. budget deficit for reference."},{"time":634000,"text":"So that might well chime"},{"time":636000,"text":"with your view that America"},{"time":638000,"text":"is a sort of warmongering military machine,"},{"time":641000,"text":"out to overpower the world"},{"time":643000,"text":"with its huge industrial-military complex."},{"time":646000,"text":"But is it true that America has the biggest military budget?"},{"time":649000,"text":"Because America is an incredibly rich country."},{"time":651000,"text":"In fact, it's so massively rich"},{"time":653000,"text":"that it can contain the four other"},{"time":655000,"text":"top industrialized nations' economies"},{"time":657000,"text":"inside itself, it's so vastly rich."},{"time":660000,"text":"So its military budget is bound to be enormous."},{"time":663000,"text":"So, to be fair and to alter our perspective,"},{"time":665000,"text":"we have to bring in another data set,"},{"time":667000,"text":"and that data set is GDP, or the country's earnings."},{"time":669000,"text":"Who has the biggest budget as a proportion of GDP?"},{"time":671000,"text":"Let's have a look."},{"time":673000,"text":"That changes the picture considerably."},{"time":676000,"text":"Other countries pop into view that you, perhaps, weren't considering,"},{"time":679000,"text":"and American drops into eighth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":681000,"text":"Now you can also do this with soldiers."},{"time":683000,"text":"Who has the most soldiers? It's got to be China."},{"time":685000,"text":"Of course, 2.1 million."},{"time":687000,"text":"Again, chiming with your view"},{"time":689000,"text":"that China has a militarized regime"},{"time":691000,"text":"ready to, you know, mobilize its enormous forces."},{"time":693000,"text":"But of course, China has an enormous population."},{"time":696000,"text":"So if we do the same,"},{"time":698000,"text":"we see a radically different picture."},{"time":700000,"text":"China drops to 124th."},{"time":702000,"text":"It actually has a tiny army"},{"time":704000,"text":"when you take other data into consideration."},{"time":707000,"text":"So, absolute figures, like the military budget,"},{"time":709000,"text":"in a connected world,"},{"time":711000,"text":"don't give you the whole picture."},{"time":713000,"text":"They're not as true as they could be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":715000,"text":"We need relative figures that are connected to other data"},{"time":718000,"text":"so that we can see a fuller picture,"},{"time":720000,"text":"and then that can lead to us changing our perspective."},{"time":722000,"text":"As Hans Rosling, the master,"},{"time":724000,"text":"my master, said,"},{"time":727000,"text":"\"Let the dataset change your mindset.\""},{"time":731000,"text":"And if it can do that, maybe it can also change your behavior."}]},{"cues":[{"time":734000,"text":"Take a look at this one."},{"time":736000,"text":"I'm a bit of a health nut."},{"time":738000,"text":"I love taking supplements and being fit,"},{"time":741000,"text":"but I can never understand what's going on in terms of evidence."},{"time":744000,"text":"There's always conflicting evidence."},{"time":746000,"text":"Should I take vitamin C? Should I be taking wheatgrass?"},{"time":748000,"text":"This is a visualization of all the evidence"},{"time":750000,"text":"for nutritional supplements."},{"time":752000,"text":"This kind of diagram is called a balloon race."},{"time":755000,"text":"So the higher up the image,"},{"time":757000,"text":"the more evidence there is for each supplement."},{"time":760000,"text":"And the bubbles correspond to popularity as regards to Google hits."},{"time":763000,"text":"So you can immediately apprehend"},{"time":766000,"text":"the relationship between efficacy and popularity,"},{"time":769000,"text":"but you can also, if you grade the evidence,"},{"time":772000,"text":"do a \"worth it\" line."},{"time":774000,"text":"So supplements above this line are worth investigating,"},{"time":777000,"text":"but only for the conditions listed below,"},{"time":780000,"text":"and then the supplements below the line"},{"time":783000,"text":"are perhaps not worth investigating."}]},{"cues":[{"time":785000,"text":"Now this image constitutes a huge amount of work."},{"time":788000,"text":"We scraped like 1,000 studies from PubMed,"},{"time":791000,"text":"the biomedical database,"},{"time":793000,"text":"and we compiled them and graded them all."},{"time":796000,"text":"And it was incredibly frustrating for me"},{"time":798000,"text":"because I had a book of 250 visualizations to do for my book,"},{"time":801000,"text":"and I spent a month doing this,"},{"time":803000,"text":"and I only filled two pages."},{"time":805000,"text":"But what it points to"},{"time":807000,"text":"is that visualizing information like this"},{"time":809000,"text":"is a form of knowledge compression."},{"time":811000,"text":"It's a way of squeezing an enormous amount"},{"time":813000,"text":"of information and understanding"},{"time":815000,"text":"into a small space."},{"time":817000,"text":"And once you've curated that data, and once you've cleaned that data,"},{"time":819000,"text":"and once it's there,"},{"time":821000,"text":"you can do cool stuff like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":823000,"text":"So I converted this into an interactive app,"},{"time":825000,"text":"so I can now generate this application online --"},{"time":827000,"text":"this is the visualization online --"},{"time":829000,"text":"and I can say, \"Yeah, brilliant.\""},{"time":831000,"text":"So it spawns itself."},{"time":833000,"text":"And then I can say, \"Well, just show me the stuff"},{"time":835000,"text":"that affects heart health.\""},{"time":837000,"text":"So let's filter that out."},{"time":839000,"text":"So heart is filtered out, so I can see if I'm curious about that."},{"time":842000,"text":"I think, \"No, no. I don't want to take any synthetics,"},{"time":844000,"text":"I just want to see plants and --"},{"time":847000,"text":"just show me herbs and plants. I've got all the natural ingredients.\""},{"time":850000,"text":"Now this app is spawning itself"},{"time":852000,"text":"from the data."},{"time":854000,"text":"The data is all stored in a Google Doc,"},{"time":856000,"text":"and it's literally generating itself from that data."},{"time":859000,"text":"So the data is now alive; this is a living image,"},{"time":861000,"text":"and I can update it in a second."},{"time":863000,"text":"New evidence comes out. I just change a row on a spreadsheet."},{"time":865000,"text":"Doosh! Again, the image recreates itself."},{"time":869000,"text":"So it's cool."},{"time":871000,"text":"It's kind of living."}]},{"cues":[{"time":874000,"text":"But it can go beyond data,"},{"time":876000,"text":"and it can go beyond numbers."},{"time":878000,"text":"I like to apply information visualization"},{"time":880000,"text":"to ideas and concepts."},{"time":883000,"text":"This is a visualization"},{"time":885000,"text":"of the political spectrum,"},{"time":887000,"text":"an attempt for me to try"},{"time":889000,"text":"and understand how it works"},{"time":891000,"text":"and how the ideas percolate down"},{"time":893000,"text":"from government into society and culture,"},{"time":895000,"text":"into families, into individuals, into their beliefs"},{"time":898000,"text":"and back around again in a cycle."},{"time":901000,"text":"What I love about this image"},{"time":903000,"text":"is it's made up of concepts,"},{"time":905000,"text":"it explores our worldviews"},{"time":907000,"text":"and it helps us -- it helps me anyway --"},{"time":909000,"text":"to see what others think,"},{"time":911000,"text":"to see where they're coming from."},{"time":913000,"text":"And it feels just incredibly cool to do that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":916000,"text":"What was most exciting for me"},{"time":919000,"text":"designing this"},{"time":921000,"text":"was that, when I was designing this image,"},{"time":923000,"text":"I desperately wanted this side, the left side,"},{"time":926000,"text":"to be better than the right side --"},{"time":928000,"text":"being a journalist, a Left-leaning person --"},{"time":931000,"text":"but I couldn't, because I would have created"},{"time":933000,"text":"a lopsided, biased diagram."},{"time":936000,"text":"So, in order to really create a full image,"},{"time":939000,"text":"I had to honor the perspectives on the right-hand side"},{"time":942000,"text":"and at the same time, uncomfortably recognize"},{"time":945000,"text":"how many of those qualities were actually in me,"},{"time":948000,"text":"which was very, very annoying and uncomfortable."},{"time":950000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":954000,"text":"But not too uncomfortable,"},{"time":956000,"text":"because there's something unthreatening"},{"time":959000,"text":"about seeing a political perspective,"},{"time":961000,"text":"versus being told or forced to listen to one."},{"time":964000,"text":"You're capable of holding conflicting viewpoints"},{"time":967000,"text":"joyously when you can see them."},{"time":969000,"text":"It's even fun to engage with them"},{"time":971000,"text":"because it's visual."},{"time":973000,"text":"So that's what's exciting to me,"},{"time":975000,"text":"seeing how data can change my perspective"},{"time":977000,"text":"and change my mind midstream --"},{"time":979000,"text":"beautiful, lovely data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":983000,"text":"So, just to wrap up,"},{"time":985000,"text":"I wanted to say"},{"time":987000,"text":"that it feels to me that design is about solving problems"},{"time":989000,"text":"and providing elegant solutions,"},{"time":992000,"text":"and information design is about"},{"time":994000,"text":"solving information problems."},{"time":996000,"text":"It feels like we have a lot of information problems"},{"time":998000,"text":"in our society at the moment,"},{"time":1000000,"text":"from the overload and the saturation"},{"time":1002000,"text":"to the breakdown of trust and reliability"},{"time":1004000,"text":"and runaway skepticism and lack of transparency,"},{"time":1006000,"text":"or even just interestingness."},{"time":1008000,"text":"I mean, I find information just too interesting."},{"time":1010000,"text":"It has a magnetic quality that draws me in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1014000,"text":"So, visualizing information"},{"time":1016000,"text":"can give us a very quick solution to those kinds of problems."},{"time":1019000,"text":"Even when the information is terrible,"},{"time":1021000,"text":"the visual can be quite beautiful."},{"time":1024000,"text":"Often we can get clarity"},{"time":1027000,"text":"or the answer to a simple question very quickly,"},{"time":1029000,"text":"like this one,"},{"time":1031000,"text":"the recent Icelandic volcano."},{"time":1034000,"text":"Which was emitting the most CO2?"},{"time":1036000,"text":"Was it the planes or the volcano,"},{"time":1038000,"text":"the grounded planes or the volcano?"},{"time":1040000,"text":"So we can have a look."},{"time":1042000,"text":"We look at the data and we see:"},{"time":1044000,"text":"Yep, the volcano emitted 150,000 tons;"},{"time":1046000,"text":"the grounded planes would have emitted"},{"time":1048000,"text":"345,000 if they were in the sky."},{"time":1051000,"text":"So essentially, we had our first carbon-neutral volcano."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1054000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1056000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1065000,"text":"And that is beautiful. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1068000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}